                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For tracking serving timeranged reads portion of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-6752&quot; title=&quot;On region server failure, serve writes and timeranged reads during the log split&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-6752&quot;&gt;HBASE-6752&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
